quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  98,8,"Jazaohum AAinda rabbihim jannatuAAadnin tajree min tahtiha al-anharu khalideenafeeha abadan radiya Allahu AAanhum waradooAAanhu thalika liman khashiya rabbah"
  99,1,"Itha zulzilati al-ardu zilzalaha"
  99,2,"Waakhrajati al-ardu athqalaha"
  99,3,"Waqala al-insanu ma laha"
  99,4,"Yawma-ithin tuhaddithu akhbaraha"
  99,5,"Bi-anna rabbaka awha laha"
  99,6,"Yawma-ithin yasduru annasuashtatan liyuraw aAAmalahum"
  99,7,"Faman yaAAmal mithqala tharratinkhayran yarah"
  99,8,"Waman yaAAmal mithqala tharratinsharran yarah"
  100,1,"WalAAadiyati dabha"
  100,2,"Falmooriyati qadha"
  100,3,"Falmugheerati subha"
  100,4,"Faatharna bihi naqAAa"
  100,5,"Fawasatna bihi jamAAa"
  100,6,"Inna al-insana lirabbihi lakanood"
  100,7,"Wa-innahu AAala thalikalashaheed"
  100,8,"Wa-innahu lihubbi alkhayri lashadeed"
  100,9,"Afala yaAAlamu itha buAAthira mafee alquboor"